</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d399n1-ptr" id="PJA11d399n1">1</a>

   <p>John Thaxter presumably brought <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Charles Adams (17701800), son of John and Abigail Adams ]">CA</abbr> on board the frigate to be entrusted to Jacksons care for the voyage to America.</p>

